    <h4>Test Early and Often</h4>
    <p>Testing early and often could mean a lot of different things at Healthentic. First, feasibility was almost always a big question that needed to be evaluated. Our goal was to create the ideal user experience, but this had to be done within the constraints of the messy heath claims data our product used.</p>

